title: OAuth 2.0 Authorization Code Flow

participant User as U
participant Browser as B
participant App Server as App
participant Auth Server as Auth
participant Resource Server as RS

U->>B: Click "Login with Google"
B->>App: GET /auth/google
App-->>B: 302 Redirect to Auth Server
B->>Auth: GET /authorize?response_type=code
Auth-->>B: Show login/consent page
U->>B: Enter credentials & grant consent
B->>Auth: POST /login (credentials)
Auth-->>B: 302 Redirect with ?code=abc123
B->>App: GET /callback?code=abc123
App->>Auth: POST /token (code, client_secret)
Auth-->>App: { access_token, refresh_token }
note right of App: Store tokens in session
App->>RS: GET /api/userinfo (Bearer token)
RS-->>App: { email, name, avatar }
App-->>B: 302 Redirect to /dashboard
B-->>U: Show logged-in dashboard
